id: pm-dc2y
title: pm templates bare command shows empty output (should list templates)
description: Running pm templates without a subcommand produces empty stdout and exit 0. Agents expecting to see a list of templates find nothing. Should default to pm templates list behavior. Fixed by adding an .action() handler to the templates command in main.ts that calls runTemplatesList.
